Repeat: sl 1 wyib, k4, pass sl-st over the 4 knit sts, p3
End Row: sl 1 wyib, k4, pass sl-st over the 4 knit sts, k1

Repeat: k1, knit 1 st under running thread between the st just worked and the next st, k1, p5
End Row: k1, knit 1 st under running thread between the st just worked and the next st, k1, p1, k1

Repeat: p3, sl 1 wyib, k4 pass sl-st over the 4 knit sts
p5, k1, knit 1 st under running thread, k1
